      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BINNAWAY WIZARD (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Flying Hugo (19.64) in a Grade 6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Speedy beginner who should be in the action early off the inside. Rates highly and will give a great sight. ADHANA MARTINA (6) settled off speed and overcame a chequered run to work home into the placings when second (19.99) at this track in a Grade 6. Safe beginner but tricky box to overcome. Expecting another bold showing. ZING MATILDA (4) will take beating coming off a quick 19.61 success at this track over 342m. Harder here but expected to feature again. SPECKED (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
